      "content": "yeah that's what i thought. i barely moved for 12 hours on the plane so my arm is definitely numb from that. the weird speech thing is probably just cuz im exhausted and my throat is dry. i dont really want to go to a hospital and wait for hours if i can just sleep it out. you're pretty sure it's just travel fatigue right? i feel okay otherwise, just a bit clumsy.",
